<br />
<br />I just cleaned some more games tonight. I don't notice any of the color fading on the connectors, and the games work just fine. I think it's best to wait until it dries, then polish it off again to get it all off. It is scary - the cloth I used to clean them comes out black. The only place I've seen this stuff for sale is WalMart - and I'd imagine they have one somewhere near you!
