	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Actually, that sort of metal polish is <strong>BAD</strong> for NES cartridges, since it will completely destroy the gold plating on the cart edge and make it <em>more</em> susceptible to corrosion. It may look nice and shiny right after you clean it, but you'll find that you need to clean it a LOT more often than you needed to previously.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


